message: So our pump did not go as planned due to the low amount of users our group has . We will be increasing this amount to atleast 3000 users and try again soon . Thanks to everyone that participated and be on the alert for the next pump 👍🏻
Pump results will be posted soon :

Pump Announcement‌ ‏ ‎ Hello everyone , we are currently working on making the channel more known to increase the pumping power for all our users , however we believe that by this date we will have enough users to attempt to pump our first coin . Good luck everyone ! ‌‌‌ ‏ ‌ ‏ ‎ Pump Details : 🕰 ‎ Time : 10/20 / 2019 18:00 GMT ‏ 💰 Exchange : ‎ Binance_CEX 🏷 ‎ Pair : BTC 🔑 Key Targets : 10 % - 30 % !

So you might be asking yourself , what exactly is a pump group ? Basically what we do is we pick a coin on binance_CEX for everyone to buy , and we send the name of that token to everyone on the group at the same time . This causes the price to increase massively due to the demand , so much that outsiders on Binance_CEX see the pump and join in . This is where you would sell the token for a profit - pumps can rise up to 50 % at a time , the more people insde the group the bigger the pump , so be sure to tell your friends about what were doing here 👍🏻

Welcome to the CMP pump group channel ! We are a brand new crypto pump and dump group and we hope to grow very fast in the very near future . If you want to help us in our journey you can help by inviting your friends to this group , hopefully we can achieve something great together 🙂
